    "把一路音频同时送到多个输出设备的 macOS 菜单栏小工具。基于 CoreAudio aggregate device，原生 SwiftUI + AppKit 互操作，无第三方依赖。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein macOS-Menüleisten-Tool, das eine Audioquelle gleichzeitig an mehrere Ausgabegeräte sendet. Baut auf CoreAudio Aggregate Device, natives SwiftUI + AppKit, ohne Drittabhängigkeiten."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A macOS menubar tool that sends one audio stream to multiple output devices at once. Built on CoreAudio aggregate devices, native SwiftUI + AppKit, no third-party dependencies."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una utilidad de la barra de menús de macOS que envía un flujo de audio a varios dispositivos a la vez. Basada en dispositivos agregados de CoreAudio, SwiftUI + AppKit nativos, sin dependencias externas."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un utilitaire de la barre des menus macOS qui envoie un flux audio vers plusieurs sorties en même temps. Basé sur les aggregate devices CoreAudio, SwiftUI + AppKit natifs, sans dépendances tierces."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un'utilità della barra dei menu di macOS che invia un flusso audio a più dispositivi contemporaneamente. Basata su CoreAudio aggregate device, SwiftUI + AppKit nativi, senza dipendenze esterne."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "1 つのオーディオを複数の出力デバイスに同時に送る macOS メニューバー小ツール。CoreAudio aggregate device 上に構築。SwiftUI + AppKit のネイティブのみ、サードパーティ依存なし。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "오디오를 여러 출력 장치로 동시에 보내는 macOS 메뉴 막대 도구. CoreAudio aggregate device 기반, 네이티브 SwiftUI + AppKit, 외부 의존성 없음."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "把一路音訊同時送到多個輸出裝置的 macOS 選單列小工具。基於 CoreAudio aggregate device，原生 SwiftUI + AppKit 互操作，無第三方依賴。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
